# Intentional: SonarQube is a public web service, 80/443 open to allowed_cidrs
# (default 0.0.0.0/0) and unrestricted egress for image pulls, dnf and ACME.
AVD-AWS-0107
AVD-AWS-0104

# Backup bucket uses SSE-S3. A customer managed KMS key is out of scope for
# the default deployment and would add cost for no threat-model benefit here.
AVD-AWS-0132

# Intentional in the complete example: the instance needs a public IP at launch
# for egress (dnf, image pulls) before the EIP association is applied.
AVD-AWS-0164
